config RAM_INGENIC_DDR_INNOPHY
	bool "Ingenic XBurst2 DDR controller + Innophy PHY"
	depends on RAM
	depends on ARCH_XBURST
	select SPL_RAM if SPL
	help
	  Driver for the Ingenic XBurst2 DDR memory controller paired with
	  the on-chip Innophy DDR PHY (Innophy IP integrated by Ingenic on
	  T40/T41/A1 and related XBurst2 SoCs). Supports DDR2, DDR3,
	  LPDDR2 and LPDDR3 chips with hardware DQS calibration enabled by
	  default. Per-variant timing tables match by DT compatible string,
	  so a single driver instance covers every T41 SKU (T41A, T41L,
	  T41LQ, T41N, T41NQ, T41XQ, T41ZG, T41ZGC, T41ZL, T41ZM, T41ZMC,
	  T41ZN, T41ZX) and the T40 family.

	  Ported from vendor U-Boot 2013 branch T41-1.2.6
	  (arch/mips/cpu/xburst2/ddr_innophy.c).
